A vintage-style illustration of an ornate brass keyhole mechanism cross-sectioned to reveal intricate clockwork gears inside, with a glowing digital certificate seal being inserted like a skeleton key. The scene is rendered in warm sepia and copper tones with aged paper texture, featuring technical blueprint-style annotations and mechanical drawings in the background. Soft golden light emanates from where the key meets the lock, suggesting successful authentication. The composition evokes Victorian-era technical illustrations merged with modern cryptographic concepts, with decorative Art Nouveau borders framing the central mechanism.
